{"id": "art-441", "label": "Art. 441", "title": "Art. 441", "slug": "art-441", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1613262945\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2451\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1613262945\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 44<sup>1</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2143592763\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2450\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2143592763\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dobândirea de c&#259;tre societate, într-un interval de\ncel mult 2 ani de la constituire sau de la autorizarea începerii <span\nclass=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\na unui bun de la un fondator ori <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionar</span>,\ncontra unei sume sau a altor contravalori reprezentând cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span>\no zecime din valoarea capitalului social subscris, va fi supus&#259;\naprob&#259;rii prealabile a adun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>,\nprecum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> prevederilor art. 38 <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 39, va fi <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionat&#259;</span>\nîn registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>, în baza actului\ntranslativ de proprietate, încheiat în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\n<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nva fi publicat&#259; în Monitorul Oficial al României, Partea a IV-a.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_289192398\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2449\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_289192398\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Nu vor fi supuse acestor prevederi <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunile</span>\nde dobândire efectuate în cadrul <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ncurente a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, cele f&#259;cute din <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;ia</span> unei <span class=SpellE>autorit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nadministrative sau a unei <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;e</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nnici cele f&#259;cute în cadrul <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunilor</span> de\nburs&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}